{"tid":1026102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將向越南提供巡防艦 助提高海上執法","createTime":"2019-02-18T00:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T07:02:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5501605a2ca8316e2e20366c8b58b7a7308aff2","tid":1026102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"美國將向越南提供巡防艦 助提高海上執法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3649264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3649264&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=1fc4be2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3649264</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍印度洋太平洋司令部司令戴維森（Philip Davidson）表示，美國和越南國防合作重點是強化越南海上執法能力，美國將移交給越南另一艘巡防艦，但未說明細節。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">越南快訊新聞網站報導，戴維森近日向美國參議院提交一份書面報告，提到越南已成為（美國）依照國際法建設印度洋太平洋地區安全秩序的重要夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n戴維森表示，目前雙方國防合作重點是強化越方海上執法能力，美方將向越方提供另一艘巡防艦。</span><br />\n<br />\n報導說，報告未說明細節，但分析人士認為，美方將依超額防衛裝備（EDA）向越南移交「漢密爾頓」級（Hamilton）巡防艦，如美國於2017年曾轉交一艘退役巡防艦「摩根紹號」（USCGC Morgenthau）給越南海警隊。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，戴維森相當重視美軍印太司令部與越南國防部的防務合作關係，將此視為「雙方關係正在發展的最良好領域之一」。戴維森表示，美國可能還向越南提供若干「掃描鷹」（Scan Eagle）無人機和T-6德州佬二型（Texan II）教練機。<br />\n<br />\n越南與美國在越戰期間是敵人，雙方於1995年關係正常化。越美雙邊貿易總額自1995年的4.51億美元增至2016年的520億美元，美國目前是越南最大出口市場。越美國防關係日益深化，美軍2018年3月曾派航空母艦「卡爾文森號」（USS Carl Vinson）訪問越南。"},{"pid":"cb8faa925d8cca9c2261edc2763c448e8961a537","tid":1026102,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:09:14.000Z","msg":"某強國比全世界圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e382fa70e82f7143a3272b3b405af13834d718e","tid":1026102,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:10:20.000Z","msg":"東亞兩個共產國家都企係侵侵果面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8309e5762f5eb9459a518917847ffe3b17eee5a","tid":1026102,"uid":37586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"工廠移晒去越南+美軍裝備<br />\n新一代亞洲強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61100737862437ef695bd11726b2f0c0a01f5910","tid":1026102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2085da27fc1c4beac6bb78aafddf09d56c9fbb7a","tid":1026102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8309e5762f5eb9459a518917847ffe3b17eee5a","tid":1026102,"uid":37586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"工廠移晒去越南+美軍裝備<br />\n新一代亞洲強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c68a2f42bc41253902cb3cad0526a3cbde0e00","tid":1026102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}